  "tags": ["standup", "hr", "slack", "ai", "productivity", "day19"],
  "notes": "## Day 19 — AI Standup Bot\n\n### Setup Instructions\n1. Import this JSON into n8n (Settings → Import Workflow)\n2. Add credentials:\n   - OpenAI API Key\n   - Google Sheets OAuth2\n   - Slack OAuth2\n3. Create a Google Sheet named 'Standups' with these columns:\n   Date | Submitted At | Employee Name | Employee Email | Team | Yesterday (Raw) | Today (Raw) | Blockers (Raw) | Mood | Blockers Detected | Blocker Summary | Blocker Severity | Risk Flag | Productivity Estimate | Sentiment | Manager Note\n4. Update the Webhook path if needed (default: /daily-standup)\n5. Activate the workflow\n\n### How Team Members Submit\nPOST to your webhook URL:\n```json\n{\n  \"employee_name\": \"Sarah Chen\",\n  \"employee_email\": \"sarah@company.com\",\n  \"team\": \"Engineering\",\n  \"what_done_yesterday\": \"Finished the user auth flow, reviewed 3 PRs, fixed the login bug\",\n  \"what_doing_today\": \"Starting the dashboard redesign, team meeting at 2pm\",\n  \"blockers\": \"Waiting on design assets from the design team\",\n  \"mood\": \"Good\",\n  \"manager_email\": \"manager@company.com\",\n  \"slack_channel\": \"#standups\",\n  \"sheets_id\": \"YOUR_SHEET_ID\"\n}\n```\n\n### What the Bot Does\n- Structures and cleans the standup update\n- Detects blockers and rates severity (none/low/medium/high)\n- Flags risky or unrealistic day plans\n- Estimates productivity level\n- Analyzes team sentiment\n- Posts formatted standup to Slack team channel\n- Fires private blocker alert to manager channel\n- Logs 16 fields to Google Sheets for team health tracking\n\n### Cost\n~$0.0003 per standup submission (GPT-4o-mini)\n\n### Gig Value\nSell as a standalone setup: $200–$600\nWith Slack bot integration + form UI: $600–$1,200"
